As was said of the Algol language, USENET seems to me a "a great
improvement on many of its successors." Web forums popped up
everywhere and then got abanonded as Yahoo-Google-Facebook groups
rose. I still feel that USENET had better mechanisms for follow-up,
private reply in email, crossposting, etc that its successors never
had.
    --The Rev. Jason Wells <jawells@iceland.freeshell.org>
      sdf.general, <ri9bsh$5qi$1@odin.sdf-eu.org>
