In short, I think it's become entirely too easy for people using
certain programming languages to use libraries from the wide world of
clowns that is the Internet. Their ecosystems make it very very easy
to become reliant on this stuff. Trouble is, those libraries are
frequently shit.

    --Rachel Kroll, "Tripping over the potholes in too many
      libraries", https://rachelbythebay.com/w/2020/08/09/lib/
